<h1>Your wallet export link</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>You just asked to export your Turf Monster wallet so you can take self-custody.
   Click the link below to view your private key on a dedicated reveal page.
   The link expires in 30 minutes and can only be used once.</p>

<p><%= link_to "Show me my private key", @export_url %></p>

<p style="color:#b91c1c;"><strong>Read this carefully before clicking.</strong>
   Once you copy your private key out of Turf Monster, anyone who gets a copy of
   it can take everything in that wallet — and we cannot recover it for you.
   Only continue when you're at a private screen, ready to paste the key into
   a wallet you trust.</p>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break:break-all;"><%= @export_url %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, ignore this message — your wallet stays
   custodial. You can reply to this email to reach <%= @support_email %>.</p>

<p>— Turf Monster</p>
